# Supported Platforms

* CentOS 7
* Ubuntu 14.04

# Parameters

* conf:
    is_server(bool): Act as NTP server
    external_servers(list of string, none): External NTP servers to use
    authorative(bool): If False, use other local servers instead of external
        ones
    authorative_servers(list): Authorative local timeservers
      ip(string): IP of the local server
    servers(list): All local timeservers
      ip(string): IP of the local server
    network:
      ip(string): IP of the network to serve
      netmask(string): Netmask of the network to serve, in dot-decimal format
